<Layout
  title="Construction Daily Report: What to Include (+ Template) | BuildWorkPro"
  description="What goes in a construction daily report: the fields every entry needs, how to tag and review it, and how digital reports protect you when a dispute surfaces."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
